+# Phase 3 — Local Fallback Plane v1
+
+## Цель
+Поднять **маленький локальный fallback LLM** только для:
+- emergency summarize
+- offline debug
+- local reports
+- работы при недоступности Vertex
+
+## Чего этот plane НЕ делает
+- не является primary LLM plane
+- не делает fleet-wide RCA
+- не делает hourly primary analysis
+- не auto-applies recommendations
+
+## Runtime
+- local Ollama API
+- gateway service в `scanner_infra`
+- режимы:
+  - `DISABLED`
+  - `FALLBACK_ONLY`
+  - `LOCAL_ONLY`
+
+## Allowed task types
+- `emergency_summarize`
+- `offline_debug`
+- `local_report`
+- `vertex_unavailable_fallback`
+
+## Streams
+- input: `stream:ml:local_fallback_requests`
+- results: `stream:ml:local_fallback_results`
+- rejections: `stream:ml:local_fallback_rejections`
+- audit: `stream:ml:local_fallback_audit`
+
+## Safe start
+```bash
+export LOCAL_FALLBACK_OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://host.docker.internal:11434
+export LOCAL_FALLBACK_OLLAMA_MODEL=<your_small_general_model>
+export LOCAL_FALLBACK_OLLAMA_CODE_MODEL=<your_small_code_model>
+export ML_LOCAL_FALLBACK_MODE=FALLBACK_ONLY
+export ML_LOCAL_FALLBACK_REQUIRE_VERTEX_DEGRADED=1
+```
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+redis-cli XADD stream:ml:local_fallback_requests * \
+  request_id lf-1 \
+  task_type emergency_summarize \
+  severity critical \
+  vertex_unavailable 1 \
+  prompt "Summarize: service degraded, Vertex unavailable, fallback engaged." \
+  ts_ms $(date +%s%3N)
+
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:local_fallback_results + - COUNT 3
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:local_fallback_rejections + - COUNT 3
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:local_fallback_audit + - COUNT 5
+curl -s localhost:9916/metrics | grep '^ml_local_fallback_'
+```
+
+## Notes
+- scope только `scanner_infra`
+- hot path не затронут
+- guardrails обязательны
